title: Decision making - Self Discipline - EURO champs
description:
Todays podcast goes into detail about how I prepare in the last 3 weeks before a marathon / championship. Cutting out sweets, alcohol etc.. and why! Also did I make mistakes this summer, both in decisions about 10k / marathon at Euro champs and how I prepared for them.

Support the show
